Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be the\Nworld's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Three-Sword\NStyle Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNow you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThree Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NZoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "The Deadly Foot\NTechnique Bursts Forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji vs. The Invincible Pearl!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NThey wanna fight, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Pops!\NYou promised me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run those pirates off,\Nthen my debt to you is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No more chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how\Nmuch more of my restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you could screw up\Nif you stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, kid, you said you were going\Nto be King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to be\NKing of the Pirates someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, I've seen a whole\Nlot of pirates in my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the first to state
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your desire so clearly\Nand without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, that back in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you were a pretty\Nawesome pirate, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you wanna be\NKing of the Pirates, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I do my best to forget\Nabout the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner of Baratie now,\Nand that's quite enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NMen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can capture that ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the Grand Line will be\Nours for the taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No more pretending\Nto be Marines...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or raising the white\Nflag of surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,None of our enemies\Nwill suspect that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we're a threat with\Na ship like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In that boat, it'll\Nalways be a sneak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. That boat\Nwould come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would think that pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,were on such a\Nridiculous-looking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but Don...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we enter the Grand Line\Nagain using that vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we come across someone\Nlike Hawk-Eye Mihawk again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,--Then what'll we do?\N--[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate the input,\NSailor, anything else? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think an\Nordinary man could
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,cut up a sailing\Nship like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That man probably has\Nthe power of the Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Although those with\NDevil Fruit powers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are rare and legendary to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you they're\Ncommonplace on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihawk must've used some\Nsort of strange power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when he sliced our\Nship to ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're on the Grand Line,\Nthose powers won't be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the straw hat freak\Nwill be considered normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThat old geezer, Red Foot Zeff,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sailed those seas for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] It stands to reason\Nthat he had strategies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for dealing with\Nthose monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The techniques for surviving\Nthat parade of weirdoes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,must be written in the\Nold man's logbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...along with clues\Nto the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is get\Nthat logbook and the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll be able to find our\Nway to the One Piece again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYa hear that, boys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's get to it!\NThat restaurant will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE cheer, yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You pirate scum are gonna\Nhafta get through us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NWe must protect the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY stammering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this thing work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This restaurant...\Nwill be a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Times like these make\Nyou reflect on your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I was meant\Nfor something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if I can make\Nit out of this alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll build a restaurant\Nas my final purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A restaurant as\Nmy final purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the control room,\Nand open up the fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No! That's a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we'll be\Ngiving the enemy a foothold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just fine.\NWe gotta do whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep those guys\Nout of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If they destroy the inside, then\Nthe old man'll complain forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say\Nsomething, you brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I said you're whiney!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm comin' for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum... Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp, yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's flying over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAnd Gum-gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--...Giant Scythe!\N--[PIRATES scream, groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja see that?! Go, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C] What's the\Nheck's up with that guy??!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NYeah! He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is crawling\Nwith guys like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay special attention\Nto how this one fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes\Noff him for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,until this fight is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So Let me get this straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're attacking the\Nrestaurant that gave you food?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got no choice but to beat\Nsome manners into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna fight on the water
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where there's no\Nplace to stand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A bold move for\Nsomeone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil Fruit has taken your\Nability to swim, hasn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but now... I'm stretchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp, cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji... Here come the fins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H]\NWhat is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] Now we have\Nsomewhere to fight 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My cooks and I will never give\Nup defending this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good plan, bringing up all\Nthat extra decking, genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we don't have to\Ntake the fight inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to damage\Nmy future ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And make no mistake,\Nit will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK I] We will never let\Nyou have the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NThat's right! We mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NWe're battle cooks now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Set sail, Mackerel Head One,\Nthe Baratie's secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So If you wanna live,\NI'd suggest running away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NWhat is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is so... cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NPaddle faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NYou paddle faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams] Those guys\Nare gonna sink me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK Z] Get 'em guys! Get 'em!\NBlow 'em away! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on\Nthe prize, Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This one counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NRight! Krieg! Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Little did you know that\Nthe Sea Restaurant Baratie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,had such a powerful weapon\Njust waiting to be unleashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] What happened?!\NDid we bump into something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NWe're not moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...the man who will\Nrule... the oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you're not... I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for\Nthese stupid games!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE shudder]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! He's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D]\NIt's coming straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant...! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG gasps]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got legs of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He kicked back that crazy boat\Njust like it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to\Ncrush your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "yeah, yeah" us,\NYou crazy fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be so smug
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if we'd been killed,\Nyou bucket of backwash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NAll right, ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you think you could wrap\Nthis up another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE growl]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES, COOKS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NYou guys still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even well armed,\Nyou're still just cooks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're expert fighters that\Nare way out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't you be\Ngood little cooks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and run along to\Na safer restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe one on land, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, guys, why are you lettin'\N'em beat you up so easily, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still call\Nyourselves fighting cooks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, these pirates\Nare really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally different from\Nthe ones we've fought before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NIt's insulting to lump us in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with that average riffraff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the great Krieg Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're the absolute\Nrulers of the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be known to all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...that this garish\Nboat already belongs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the great and\Npowerful Krieg Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your cronies will never\Nset foot in our restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHe's right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] You know what,\NI've been a cook all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked at a\Nlot of restaurants,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and gotten fired from them all\Nfor scuffling and livin' hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And after years of wandering,\Nwe finally found a home here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NAnybody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the restaurant that's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,owned by a guy name\NRed Foot Zeff, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We found this "Damn Cooks\NWanted" sign, is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NYeah... It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NBut you need to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is no\Nordinary restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't matter\Nwho they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...or where they come from...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...if someone comes in hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will feed them\Nuntil they're stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?!\NCan you handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't serve\Nanyone slop like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What'd you go\Nand hit me for, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Share victory! Share defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We like fighting and cooking,\Nso this place is perfect for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's\Nno other place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that? Now that's\Ntrue fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] Committing ourselves\Nto cooking fine cuisine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,day in and day out\Nis a fierce battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that,\Nthese pirates are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS] Yeah!\N--[PATTY] Protect Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES, COOKS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL] Just what do you\Nguys think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that? Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL laughs]\NSo... let's do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But... before we begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only fair I\Ngive you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Pearl,\Nthe Invincible Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty! Carne! Are you boys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that pair\Nis far from okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two just experienced\Nmy Pearl Surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my signature punches,\Nyou bumbling, pathetic idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE L laughs]\NHey! Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice knife...\NI think I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha? Give it here...\NC'mon, let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groan, grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy knows how to\Nkick some serious butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew there was a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked him so much\Nright off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A kitchen knife\Nis a cook's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you filthy pirates\Ntry to desecrate one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with your grubby little hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay down\Nand hang on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna teach\Nthese bozos a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling]\N--You must be out of your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think we're gonna\Nbe beaten by a mere cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you "mere cook" after
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I fillet every one\Nof you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! How very imputative of you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat them all\Nusing only your kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I to be impressed by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cook, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do my job very well\Nif I ruined my hands in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be taking you\Ndown with my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm invincible, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won all 61 of\Nmy battles completely
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and totally unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite remarkable, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever shed a single\Ndrop of my blood in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you realize my power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be a gentleman,\Nbut I'm not gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that supposed to be a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause it wasn't even\Na little bit funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropping your guard is a good\Nway to end up dead, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL] Even battleship\Ncannons don't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I come out of any\Nattack unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that could've\Nbeen really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I didn't\Nfall into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NH-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]\NThis isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a nosebleed, Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we know it's\Nnot a battle wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE P]\NSo just keep calm, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,These people aren't just\Nmean; they're dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Uh.. Wanna tell me\Nwhy everyone's freakin' out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're worried\Nabout a nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a nosebleed!\NDon't lose your cool! Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NGeez... What is that guy doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger...! Danger...! Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets upset,\Nhe catches fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Pearls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Special...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Perish in my flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With my shields and this\Ninferno, I am invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThat moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We need that ship, and\Nhe's gonna destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Ow! My butt's on fire!\N--[SANJI] Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] Oh, no! We're\Neither gonna burn or drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's destroying our only ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NThis isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant's\Ngonna catch fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NNot on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NBurn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYou son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait! No! You'll get burned!\N--[CARNE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] There's no way I'm\Ngonna let you torch our dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's either brave or dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That cook is gonna burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL] But... but... these\Nflames scare everyone away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... if I was\Nscared of fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't be much of a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL gasps]\NI hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that refined gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL  screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! He got him good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he just broke through\NPearl's invincible wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NYou stupid cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... kill... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Need more fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK AA]\NNo! The whole boat's gonna burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] If the blaze\Ngets to the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the ship will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Zeff! Get outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES, COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He put out my Fire Pearls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Pearls, eh?\NThat's kid's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! The gust from his kick\Nput out all of those flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Foot Zeff is still\Njust as strong as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Pops! I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, it's finally\Ncome down to this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice-- Smash\Nthe fins or the boat burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NSanji! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK Z] He can't escape!\NHe's surrounded by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOuchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow! Hot! Hot! Hot!\N--He tossed that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow! Fire! Hot! Ow! Ah!\N--right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearl is down! And he's not\Ngonna get up this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NNo! Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NSo weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that guy sure is goofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[bones crack] You want\Nsomething done right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...you got no choice\Nbut to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZEFF groans]\N--[LUFFY, SANJI gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NThe battle ends right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, SANJI gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NShoot him! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do\Nis kill the geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the restaurant\Nwill be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] There's no way I'm gonna\Nlet them take this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Taking a hostage!\NThat's fighting dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just asking for\Na good beat down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Butt out, Chore Boy!\NKeep your hands out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.25,0:24:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCan I use my legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I'm gonna cut\Nyou to pieces, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.59,0:24:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let the old man's\Npurpose in life be taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.76,0:24:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zeff and Sanji's Dream!\NThe Illusory All Blue!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.39,0:24:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

